The Enable Ireland Wild Atlantic Art Sale is underway!
Join us online in our virtual gallery for this unique and artistic fundraising event. We hope you enjoy browsing through our beautiful collection of pieces which have been created by artists living on, or inspired by, our island’s rugged west coast.
This event brings the raw beauty of our wild Atlantic to life. You’ll have the opportunity to purchase a unique art piece AND support a great cause, too.
Enable Ireland’s Wild Atlantic Art Sale runs into December. Thanks to all the incredible artists who have donated pieces for the sale. All profits will support our vital disability services for thousands of children and adults in Ireland.
